      USDA Organic

      USDA Organic certified products are required to be produced using farming practices that maintain and improve soil and water quality, reduce the use of synthetic materials, conserve biodiversity, and avoid genetic engineering, among other factors. Crops can be certified organic if they're grown without prohibited substances such as most synthetic fertilizers and pesticides for three years prior to harvest. Livestock are raised on pastures and treated humanely without growth hormones or antibiotics. Organic products do not contain GMOs or artificial colours, flavours or preservatives. USDA Organic products contain a minimum of 95% organic ingredients and use the USDA Organic seal.

      About this item

      • PROMOTES STRONG HAIR GROWTH - This pure batana blend hair oil is enriched with biotin, vitamin E and keratin to stimulate hair follicles and promote healthy, fast, thicker hair growth. The unique blend of rosemary batana castor oil is ideal for your quest for luscious hair.
      • ALL-NATURAL INGREDIENTS - This hair growth oil blend contains a variety of premium active and natural ingredients, pure plant ingredients, 100% pure, without any parabens or unsafe ingredients. Various ingredients work synergistically to nourish hair and achieve remarkable results.
      • SAY GOODBYE TO FRIZZY, DAMAGED, BRITTLE HAIR - Rosemary oil awakens your scalp. Black castor oil strengthens your hair. Batana oil promotes healthy hair growth. Pumpkin seed oil deeply moisturizes your hair. Sweet almond oil smooths your hair. Ginger and mint stimulate your follicles. Keratin increases your hair's elasticity. All of these ingredients work together to bring your hair back to life!
      • LIGHTWEIGHT HAIR OIL FORMULA - This lightweight, non-greasy blend of hair oils contains antioxidants and essential fatty acids that quickly provide your hair with the nutrients it needs. It is refreshing and leaves no oily residue. It can be used on long, short, straight, or curly hair.
      • DRIP TIP & COMB APPLICATOR This Batana Rosemary Blend Hair Growth Oil can revitalize your hair. The drip tip and comb applicator make the application process more convenient.

      How customer reviews and ratings work

      Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

      To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

      Amazon Customer
      5 out of 5 stars
      Totally Worth for Try
      been using this hair oil for about 3 weeks now The scent is really nice, not too overpowering, which I appreciate. It has a subtle, pleasant smell that doesn't clash with my other hair products or perfume. Some hair oils can be really heavy or medicinal smelling, but this one just smells clean and fresh. As for what it does, I mainly got it to help with dry ends and a bit of frizz. It's been working pretty well! My hair feels softer and looks shinier without being greasy. I use about 2-3 drops on damp hair after showering, and sometimes a tiny bit on dry hair if I need to tame flyaways during the day. The bottle itself is nice, sturdy bottle with a dropper that makes it easy to control how much you're using. Not too big or bulky, fits fine in my bathroom cabinet. Results-wise, I've noticed my hair looks healthier overall. The ends aren't as dry and raggedy looking as they were before.

      • LIGHTWEIGHT HAIR OIL FORMULA - This lightweight, non-greasy blend of hair oils contains antioxidants and essential fatty acids that quickly provide your hair with the nutrients it needs. It is refreshing and leaves no oily residue. It can be used on long, short, straight, or curly hair.
      • DRIP TIP & COMB APPLICATOR This Batana Rosemary Blend Hair Growth Oil can revitalize your hair. The drip tip and comb applicator make the application process more convenient.

      Product Description

      AKBAN Hair Growth Oil is a nutrient-rich blend of 100% pure Batana, Castor, Rosemary, and Pumpkin Seed Oils that nourishes and strengthens hair from root to tip. Infused with Biotin, Keratin, and Vitamin E, it helps reduce breakage, improve shine, and support fuller, healthier- looking hair. Lightweight and non-greasy, this oil absorbs quickly, leaving hair soft, smooth, and manageable. Safe for all hair types and free from parabens, sulfates, and mineral oils, its a clean, plant-based treatment for natural hair growth and restoration.

      For external use only.

      Apply a small amount of oil to your scalp and hair, massaging it in gently. Use daily for best results.
